| `{{BRAND_NAME}}` | Official brand name, exact casing | `12eat唐人街外卖` |
| `{{BRAND_SLUG}}` | Lowercase alphanumeric, no spaces | `12eat` |
| `{{BRAND_NICHE}}` | One-sentence positioning | `Authentic Chinese food delivery` |
| `{{BRAND_MISSION}}` | Agent's core mission | `Generate posts that drive orders` |
| `{{MARKETS}}` | Target markets + languages | `North America (en) + 海外华人社区 (zh)` |
| ~~`{{OWNER_LARK_ID}}`~~ | Removed — all Lark users are team | — |
